snippet.title: Down to One - Greenlight Trailer
snippet.description:
Vote for Down to One on Steam Greenlight: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=320845390

NOTE: All footage is captured from an in-game pre-alpha build, certain models and animations are not final.

Down To One on Reddit: http://www.reddit.com/r/DownToOne/

Down To One on Twitter https://twitter.com/downtoonegame

42 players start. Only 1 can survive. Down to One is a competitive survival combat game, where players can use anything in the immersive, open-world environment to survive and outlast their competition.
